      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780120584845,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "課題1【解決】rail は「召喚式」だった — ホットキーで呼ぶ→操作→閉じる（Mission Control 型）",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "課題1【解決】rail は「召喚式」だった — ホットキーで呼ぶ→操作→閉じる（Mission Control 型）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "syncedAt": "2026-05-30T06:00:41.204Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-05-30T06:00:41.195Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "mprwbza6sp6iec3pkmj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 104,
      "y": 1154,
      "width": 740.671875,
      "height": 13.799999999999999,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b22",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1069295117,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1597186915,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780120584845,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "つまり常設じゃない。Grid と同じで一時的に画面へ重ねるだけ → 場所の予約問題は起きない。下の②③は「もし常設だったら」の参考。",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "つまり常設じゃない。Grid と同じで一時的に画面へ重ねるだけ → 場所の予約問題は起きない。下の②③は「もし常設だったら」の参考。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "syncedAt": "2026-05-30T06:00:41.204Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-05-30T06:00:41.195Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "mprwbza6hmev72q2c3o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 128,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 200.79541015625,
      "height": 14.95,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
